<plot>Elvis impersonators now number more than 35,000 worldwide. Almost Elvis investigates this cultural phenomenon with humor and insight. Filmed all over America, it traces the journeys of several hopefuls to the world's largest Elvis impersonator contest and documents their quest to create the perfect illusion of the King of Rock'n'Roll.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?032303</url></doc>
